content:
You must have a Salesforce FSC license, a Policy Administration license, and a Claims Management license to use all features in the Insurance Industries Extension package.

Complete tasks in this order:

Install the Insurance and Vlocity Health Managed Package. This contains data model extensions, Apex Insurance services, templates, cards, Lightning components, product modeling components, and rating engine components.

Install the Insurance Industries Extension Managed Package. Enable Policy Administration and Claims Management before installing if you have add-on licenses for them. 

If you use group benefits, see Give Users Access to Group Benefits in the Salesforce Data Model.
title: Installing and Upgrading Insurance in Salesforce
